<strong>BIBLIOGRAPHY ENTRY</strong>
<br><br>
Add a bibliography at the end of your essay citing all relevant sources used in your research, 
regardless of whether they are explicitly mentioned in your writing.
<br><br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br><br>
For more detailed information on other elements that may be included in multimedia citation see Chicago Manual of Style <a href="http://www.chicagomanualofstyle.org.ezproxy.uws.edu.au/book/ed17/part3/ch14/psec261.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">14.261</a>.
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent double-line-spacing">
	Performer(s) surname, given name. <em>Title of Work</em>. Medium of publication. Directed by Director(s) given name and surname. Location of publisher: Publisher, year of publication.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent double-line-spacing">
	<span class="hover" title="Performer(s) surname, given name">Hamilton, Marc, Harry Sunford, Cassy Fisher, Peter Cushion and Alec Stout</span>. 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of Work">Star Warts</span></em>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Medium of publication">Motion picture</span>. 
	Directed by 
	<span class="hover" title="Director(s) surname, given name">Jeff Lucas</span>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Location of publisher">Los Angeles</span>: 
	<span class="hover" title="Publisher">20th Century Floss</span>, 
	<span class="hover" title="year of publication">1977</span>.
</blockquote>
<br>
If you are citing a commentary or scene, cite it as though you would cite a book chapter.
<br><br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent double-line-spacing">
	<span class="hover" title="Performer(s) surname, given name">Hamilton, Marc, Harry Sunford, Cassy Fisher, Peter Cushion and Alec Stout</span>. 
	&#34;<span class="hover" title="commentary or scene">The search for the secret plans</span>&#34;. 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of Work">Star Warts</span></em>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Medium of publication">Motion picture</span>. 
	Directed by 
	<span class="hover" title="Director(s) surname, given name">Jeff Lucas</span>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Location of publisher">Los Angeles</span>: 
	<span class="hover" title="Publisher">20th Century Floss</span>, 
	<span class="hover" title="year of publication">1977</span>.
</blockquote>
